data.title: Special Awards – Aloha Section
data.text: Each year the Aloha Section PGA Foundation, a non-profit 501(c)(3) charitable organization, partners with Friends of Hawaii Charities, Inc. to honor the players, volunteers, and supporters of Hawaii’s lead golf associations. This celebration awards those who have displayed the best competitive skill, countless hours of selfless service, development of growth for the game, and other charitable contributions.
